\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4134619\charrsid29954 else\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7431414\charrsid29954  washing, she got hold of the paraffin like you do now and chucked it on top o
