en you fill it with sticks so instead of seeing it proper out, no, she wouldn't do it, she got the paraffin, it all come up at her see. Oh she was in hospital for a long time. Hospital, that was - you know where Whittles is - you down through Whittles and
 there's a big - big red brick house isn't there, with a walled in front. That was the hospital in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Weymouth{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
 then. Before we went up this one where it is now. 'Cos my Olive - our Olive there - she had operation there for - for a rupture. That's how I know where it is.
