\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4134619\charrsid29954 squeeze}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7431414\charrsid29954 , like that, and then - chuck them up top somewhere.
