No, we never helped. No fear. We never had irons like they've got now you know. Yes, there's one down there keeping the door open now. But that's only a small iron
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2562708 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7431414\charrsid29954 Was any of the washing sent out?
