hatter and clothiers. And to make two ends meet do you know what he used to do? He used to breed canaries and - birds and that and - buy a cage for a shilling, and sell 'em, couple of bob, half a crown. Fpo to make two ends meet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2562708 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7431414\charrsid29954 So you came down here to Fortuneswell to buy clothing?
