Oh religion. Oh yes. I had to attend church, had to look after that lot. Otherwise you could do whatever - be like devils but you had to go to church.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2562708 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7431414\charrsid29954 And you went three times?
