 George's and he used to walk right over - whether it was Saturday or Sunday. And sweat, I used to see him coming in sweating - his surplice he had in the vestry. Well he had a blinking habit you know if we never scurried out of the vestry he used to - he
'd have us. You'd see old Griggs looking at you over the glass like this. Oh he had a proper habit of falling down like that you know.
