Yes, every Friday night. Clean clothes and all. And all lot was put one side ready for Monday morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2562708 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7431414\charrsid29954 Changed all bedclothes as well?
