Yes. Old Ned - bank man I remember I talk about old Ned Scriven, he died down - down Wakenham. And - there was our Uncle Jack, he - he died - 1969 somewhere about that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2562708 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7431414\charrsid29954 So in 1911 you were about nine?
