Oh the undertakers. Undertaker, he'd lay it out and sometimes this - the women'd go about, do nothing else only lay people out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2562708 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7431414\charrsid29954 Do you remember there being any women like this?
